{"tid":2148425,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"死亡率1.56% 勢超H3N2流感  醫生：邊境穿窿 長者送命","createTime":"2020-08-10T02:33:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T02:35:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b8cae558163b484100b426ab54534c8f0ccbf092","tid":2148425,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T02:33:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200810/236623MKORWFYNPKWACNI4VEVM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200810%2F236623MKORWFYNPKWACNI4VEVM%2F&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25YklZDiKRLpOq3%2FNqhGVOPOo%3D&h=21091144\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200810%2F236623MKORWFYNPKWACNI4VEVM%2F&h=d0974906\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200810/236623MKORWFYNPKWACNI4VEVM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n死亡率1.56% 勢超H3N2流感 <br />\n醫生：邊境穿窿 長者送命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FgkgXuarQ67bKHX8U0vZLVzjANQ=/573x499/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WAQZ4YOPZ4POMSM6NE5VJA5HTY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFgkgXuarQ67bKHX8U0vZLVzjANQ%3D%2F573x499%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWAQZ4YOPZ4POMSM6NE5VJA5HTY.gif&h=288febdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n耆康會啟業護理安老院再有院友染疫，全院40多名院友需撤離檢疫。王子俊攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港昨新增72宗武漢肺炎確診個案，累計4,080人染疫。醫管局公佈昨日有五名患者離世，他們全屬有長期病患的長者，疫潮至今已有52人死亡，本港死亡率升至1.27%，單計第三波疫潮更達1.56%。有感染及傳染病專科醫生歸咎政府未有做好邊境防疫，導致老人院舍爆疫致多人死亡，他警告由於疫情持續，不排除最終死亡率高於數年前大爆發的冬季流感。<br />\n<br />\n昨日再多72宗確診，63宗是本地感染，包括33宗經家人或朋友飯敍染疫，24宗源頭未明；初步確診約有40宗。同日有五名病人死。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n瑪麗醫院81歲男病人（第3714號個案）居於維港灣5座，早前疑因為與一名確診者（第2282號個案）同病房，而該確診者曾於房內多次未戴好口罩，懷疑他因此受感染。<br />\n<br />\n體弱者易現細胞因子風暴<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：斥政府拒封關釀禍  蔡堅︰須吸取教訓<br />\n<br />\n屯門康和護老中心一名78歲女院友（第2955號個案）早上5時37分離世，該護老院至今累計七人病歿。<br />\n<br />\n另一名死者是第2131號個案、一。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n上述死者均有長期病患，疫情至今，本港累計52名患者逝世，死亡率為1.27%。若單以第三波疫情計算，更高達1.56%，死者全部是60至95歲，大多有長期病患。<br />\n<br />\n感染及傳染病專科醫生曾祈殷表示，長者及長期病患者確診武漢肺炎後，會出現細胞因子風暴，令免疫系統過份活躍，引發急性呼吸。。。。。。。。。。」<br />\n<br />\n疫情何時結束仍是。。。。。。。。。。/15年冬季爆發H3N2流感時，死亡率達3.88%。曾認為政府與其有資源做全民檢測，倒不如集中資源為邊境，為所有入境人士檢測。<br />\n<br />\n病人政策連線主席林志釉促請政府仿效2003年政府成立「沙士信託基金」，為。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/T6J_vCoYfHfXS97Af6m9xP6Rvz8=/998x599/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IEUWFUGR2KTQE4Q65PT7P4OCUY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FT6J_vCoYfHfXS97Af6m9xP6Rvz8%3D%2F998x599%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIEUWFUGR2KTQE4Q65PT7P4OCUY.gif&h=37f8b5bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/T8zjiYpfB5DcLGnyzbUMVJQfT30=/1290x557/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HWNOZPN4S7B5GWXL2JO37GEXPI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FT8zjiYpfB5DcLGnyzbUMVJQfT30%3D%2F1290x557%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHWNOZPN4S7B5GWXL2JO37GEXPI.gif&h=4247966b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc0915b6e72f0cb3347b55d96fcb5f102c7f3b12","tid":2148425,"uid":31237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T02:35:35.000Z","msg":"冬季爆發H3N2流感時 死亡率達3.88%"}]}